<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="<%= lang %>">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>How It Works - Furry Tails Photography</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include("navbar") %>

  <main>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="how-it-works-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="hero-content">
          <div class="hero-text">
            <h2 style="margin-top: 15px;">This is how we'll create those bright, happy pet portraits.</h2>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 5px;">Don't worry if your pet is energetic, easly distractes or "doesn't listen". That's completely normal - and we work with it.</p>
            <a href="/<%= lang %>/contact" class="btn-primary">BOOK NOW →</a>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-image">
            <img src="/gallery/Gallery1.jpg" alt="Pet">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Before Your Session Section -->
    <section class="session-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="session-wrapper session-before">
          <div class="session-left">
            <h2><span class="session-badge">01.</span> BEFORE THE SESSION</h2>
            <p><strong>Getting ready is simple:</strong></p>

            <ul>
              <li>Let's talk.</li>
              <li>First I'd love to find out more about your pet, so I know what to expect and how to approach the session.</li>
              <li>I also want to hear about what you're looking for and what kind of photos you like — and just as importantly, what you don't.</li>
              <li>We'll decide on the details together — things like background colours, mood, and anything else that matters to you.</li>
              <li>If you already have ideas, I'd love to hear about them.</li>
            </ul>


            <div class="session-important-box">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/>
              </svg>
              <div>
                <p><strong>The most important thing?</strong></p>
                <p>Bring treats. And don't overfeed your pet beforehand — a little motivation goes a long way.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="session-right">
            <img src="/gallery/session2.jpg" alt="Before your session">
            <div class="session-overlay">
              <p><strong>You're welcome to bring:</strong></p>
              <div class="overlay-items">
                <div class="overlay-item">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-panda-icon lucide-panda"><path d="M11.25 17.25h1.5L12 18z"/><path d="m15 12 2 2"/><path d="M18 6.5a.5.5 0 0 0-.5-.5"/><path d="M20.69 9.67a4.5 4.5 0 1 0-7.04-5.5 8.35 8.35 0 0 0-3.3 0 4.5 4.5 0 1 0-7.04 5.5C2.49 11.2 2 12.88 2 14.5 2 19.47 6.48 22 12 22s10-2.53 10-7.5c0-1.62-.48-3.3-1.3-4.83"/><path d="M6 6.5a.495.495 0 0 1 .5-.5"/><path d="m9 12-2 2"/></svg>
                  <span>Favorite toys</span>
                </div>
                <div class="overlay-item">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-shirt-icon lucide-shirt"><path d="M20.38 3.46 16 2a4 4 0 0 1-8 0L3.62 3.46a2 2 0 0 0-1.34 2.23l.58 3.47a1 1 0 0 0 .99.84H6v10c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h8a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V10h2.15a1 1 0 0 0 .99-.84l.58-3.47a2 2 0 0 0-1.34-2.23z"/></svg>
                  <span>Outfits or costumes</span>
                </div>
                <div class="overlay-item">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-star-icon lucide-star"><path d="M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.53.53 0 0 1-.77-.56l.881-5.139a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-.611-1.879L2.16 9.795a.53.53 0 0 1 .294-.906l5.165-.755a2.122 2.122 0 0 0 1.597-1.16z"/></svg>
                  <span>Anything that shows personality</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- During Your Session Section -->
    <section class="session-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="session-wrapper session-during">
          <div class="session-left">
            <h2><span class="session-badge">02.</span> DURING THE SESSION</h2>
            <p>Sessions take place in my home studio, not in a big commercial space—It's a comfortable, pet-friendly setup where pets settle in quickly.</p>

            <p><strong>WHAT TO EXPECT:</strong></p>
            <ul>
              <li>Professional lighting, laid back atmosphere.</li>
              <li>Cosy home-like environment.</li>
              <li>You stay involved the whole time - your presence helps your pet feel safe.</li>
              <li>We follow a natural flow that works for your pet. We start simple - something easy to help your pet relax and understand what's going on like sitting, lying down. Then we gradually build up to more playful, energetic moments</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="session-right">
            <img src="/gallery/session1.jpg" alt="During the session">
            <div class="session-overlay">
              <p><strong>Think:</strong></p>
              <div class="overlay-items">
                <div class="overlay-item">
                  <span>Jumping</span>
                </div>
                <div class="overlay-item">
                  <span>Playing</span>
                </div>
                <div class="overlay-item">
                  <span>Catching treats</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- After the Session Section -->
    <section class="session-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="session-wrapper session-after">
          <div class="session-left">
            <h2><span class="session-badge">03.</span> AFTER THE SESSION</h2>
            <p>Whithin two weeks, you'll recive a link to your personal gallery, where you'll be able to view and choose your favourite images. I will then carefully edit them for you and get the prints you chose.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="session-right">
            <img src="/gallery/session3.jpg" alt="After the session">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include('footer') %>
</body>
</html>
